* === Ch3: KE Duty-Cycle (RX only) ===
V_ke ke_raw 0 DC 12
R_kp ke_raw dp3 680
R_rx3 dp3 oa3 1k
X_or3 oa3 0 mr3 0 TLP521
R_pu3 v3_bus mr3 13k

* === ANALOG CONDITIONING ===
R_bdh vin_prot bat_div 10k
R_bdl bat_div 0 2.2k
D_bch bat_div v3_bus
D_bcl 0 bat_div
R_bbo adc_bat_raw adc_bat 1k
C_bf adc_bat 0 100n
R_ba adc_bat 0 10Meg

V_af air_raw 0 DC 2.5
R_adh air_raw air_div 10k
R_adl air_div 0 10k
D_ach air_div v3_bus
D_acl 0 air_div
R_abo adc_air_raw adc_air 1k
C_af adc_air 0 100n
R_aa adc_air 0 10Meg

* === MCU LOAD ===
R_mcu v3_bus 0 330
